		record both in array of stations
		set array of times each station started at to begin 1, 0
		set array of times each station ended at to begin 0, 1
	otherwise
		record just the start station in array of stations
		set array of times each station started at to begin 1
		set array of times each station ended at to begin 1
	loop through every data entry beginning at the second
		set counters for if start and end stations match any existing station to false
		loop through array of visited stations
			check if current station in array of stations is equal to the start station of current data entry
				change variable tracking if start station has been visited before to true
				increment the number of times this station has been started at
			check if current station in array of stations is equal to the end station of current data entry
				change variable tracking if end station has been visited before to true
				increment the number of times this station has been ended at
			check if start station and end station have both been visited before using the variables tracking that
				break out of stations loop
		check if start station was not a match for any visited stations and end station was
